061000******************************************************************
061100*
061200 020-E-PROCESSA.
061300
061400
061500
061600     MOVE    SPACES                  TO      AREA-IN
061700                                             AREA-OUT.
061800
061900     RECEIVE COMS-IN MESSAGE         INTO    AREA-IN.
062000
062100     IF      COMS-IN-STATUS          =       00 OR 89 OR 92 OR
062200                                             93 OR 97
062300             NEXT    SENTENCE
062400     ELSE
