064200
064300     ACCEPT  AX-DATA-MAQ             FROM    DATE YYYYMMDD.
064400
064500     IF      IN-CODE                 =       "V442"
064600             PERFORM 030-E-V442      THRU    030-S-V442
064700     ELSE
064800             MOVE    239             TO      IA1.
064900
065000
