115300                    MOVE   "S"       TO     AX-ALTEROU
115400     ELSE
115500        IF   AX-ALFA                 IS     ALPHABETIC
115600             SEARCH  TBA-LET-NUM     AT     END
115700                     MOVE   "N"      TO     AX-ALTEROU
115800             WHEN    TBA-LET (IN1)   =      AX-ALFA
115900                   MOVE    TBA-NUM (IN1)    TO  AX-ALFA-ALTER
116000                   MOVE   "S"        TO     AX-ALTEROU.
